skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: chicago vegan
des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in Chicago. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Chicago Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Chicago Vegan for a fact."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
